Load Packages
```{r, include=FALSE}
library(tidyverse)
library(lubridate)
```

Read in the data
```{r, include=FALSE}
garfs <- read_csv("Garfs CSV")
```
Parse Dates
```{r, include=FALSE}
garfs$Date <- mdy(garfs$Date)
```

Inspect
```{r}
str(garfs)
```

```{r}
summary(garfs)
```
```{r, echo=TRUE}
head(garfs)
```


Test dates
```{r}
month(garfs)
```
